8 An Act relating to schools; amending 70 O.S. 2021,
Section 5-132, as amended by Section 1, Chapter 162,
9 O.S.L. 2024 (70 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 5-132),
which relates to adult high school completion;
10 extending age of individuals allowed to complete high
school; updating statutory language; allowing a
11 school district that provides a full-time virtual
education program to provide instruction to persons
12 up to certain age if the persons receive instruction
by certain method; exempting certain students from
13 being included in certain reports; providing an
