18 amended by Section 1, Chapter 162, O.S.L. 2024 (70 O.S. Supp. 2024,
19 Section 5-132), is amended to read as follows:
20 Section 5-132. A. Any person who is of legal age and a
21 resident of this state, over the age of twenty-one (21) and under
22 the age of twenty-six (26) thirty (30), and who has not completed
23 the twelfth grade in school shall be given the same educational
24 privileges and opportunities provided by law for children over the
