18 B. Any resident of the state who is age nineteen (19) years of
19 age or older, who is not enrolled in any high school program, and
20 who has not completed the twelfth grade may attend any adult high
21 school completion program which is established by a school district
22 and approved by the State Board of Career and Technology Education
23 if such attendance has the approval of the district offering the
24 program. Such attendance shall not be counted in the average daily
